            "notes": "The deck focuses on using powerful reanimation spells and sacrificing creatures to fuel aggressive plays and overwhelm the opponent quickly. Emet-Selch, Unsundered acts as the commander to support the strategy of bringing back powerful creatures such as Archon of Cruelty and Emperor of Bones from the graveyard to the battlefield. The deck includes a variety of spells to enable this gameplay, including Animate Dead, Dance of the Dead, and Necromancy. Additionally, there are disruptive spells like Thoughtseize and Duress to control the opponent's hand and remove threats. The goal is to quickly assemble a board presence and close out the game before the opponent has a chance to stabilize."
